{{Vgname|智慧之海|原名：Abzû或ABZÛ|en=Ocean of Wisdom}}由Giant Squid Studios開發，並由[[505_Games|505 Games]]發行的[[冒险游戏|冒险游戏]]，遊戲發行於[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]，[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]，[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]以及[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]，最初於2016年8月發布數位版，適用於遊戲機的實體版於2017年1月正式推出，並於2018年11月發售任天堂Switch版本。遊戲中要操控潛水員探索海洋並使用魔法之泉恢復自然生命，玩家可以自由探索露天水域，天然洞穴或古老遺蹟的水下環境。

遊戲發展歷時三年，由十三人的團隊共同開發。幾位成員包括導演 Matt Nava 和作曲家[[Austin_Wintory|Austin Wintory]]曾經製作2012年的電子遊戲《[[风之旅人|风之旅人]]》。Abzû的海洋環境中，結合了對《风之旅人》中沙漠環境，和受到 Nava 對水肺潛水的熱愛。Abzû在銷售排行榜上名列前茅，得到了評論家的好評：大多數讚譽美術風格，並與“风之旅人”進行比較。

== 游戏内容 ==
玩家扮演着[[潜水|潜水员]]的角色探索古老的科技遗址和淹没的[[廢墟|废墟]]、周围充满动植物的水下环境。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Abzu review|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-08-02-abzu-review|accessdate=2020-03-28|date=2016-08-02|last=Gaston|first=Martin|work=Eurogamer|language=en|archive-date=2020-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328012148/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-08-02-abzu-review|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Abzu Review|url=https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/abzu-review/1900-6416489/|accessdate=2020-03-28|work=GameSpot|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328010648/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/abzu-review/1900-6416489/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在一些地区，潜水员还能够探索水上的陆地环境。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Abzu review|url=https://www.polygon.com/2016/8/2/12290330/abzu-review-ps4-pc-playstation-4|accessdate=2020-03-28|date=2016-08-02|last=McElroy|first=Justin|work=Polygon|language=en|archive-date=2020-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328010648/https://www.polygon.com/2016/8/2/12290330/abzu-review-ps4-pc-playstation-4|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 历史和设计 ==
[[索尼電腦娛樂|索尼電腦娛樂]]在2014年[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]的新聞發佈會上宣佈了 Abzû，[[游戏开发者|游戏开发]]商"Giant Squid"製作的第一款遊戲，由《[[花_(游戏)|花]]》和《[[风之旅人|風之旅人]]》的藝術總監Matt Nava担任创意总监和艺术总监，《风之旅人》的配乐[[Austin_Wintory|Austin Wintory]]也为游戏制作配乐。游戏由[[505_Games|505 Games]]在[[PS4|PS4]]和[[Microsoft_Windows| Windows]] 上發佈<ref name = "gs1">{{citation| title = E3 2014: Debut Game from Journey Art Director's Studio Announced, Called Abzu| first = Carolyn| last = Petit| date = 2014-06-09| url = http://www.gamespot.com/articles/e3-2014-debut-game-from-journey-art-director-s-studio-announced-called-abzu/1100-6420282/| work = [[Gamespot|Gamespot]]| accessdate = 2016-08-06| archive-date = 2014-09-15| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140915092712/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/e3-2014-debut-game-from-journey-art-director-s-studio-announced-called-abzu/1100-6420282/| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="ign2014">{{citation| url = http://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/06/10/e3-2014-505-games-announces-abzu| title = E3 2014: 505 Games Announces Abzu| first = Leah B.| last = Jackson| work = [[IGN|IGN]]| date = 2014-06-09| accessdate = 2016-08-06| archive-date = 2019-10-01| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191001214128/https://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/06/10/e3-2014-505-games-announces-abzu| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

其名稱來源於[[苏美尔|苏美尔]]神话，由“Ab”（海洋） 和“Zû”（已知）组成，意被解釋為"智慧的海洋"。<ref name="et">{{citation | url = http://www.abzugame.com/ | title = ABZÛ | work = www.abzugame.com | accessdate = 2016-08-03 | quote = The name references a concept from the oldest mythologies; it is the combination of the two ancient words AB, meaning ocean, and ZÛ, meaning to know. ABZÛ is the ocean of wisdom | archive-date = 2017-01-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170129043131/http://www.abzugame.com/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

游戏最别具风格的地方是以游泳模拟器，把重点放在探索和平與和人类互动的水生动物。它模拟鱼和魚之间的繁殖和掠夺行为，并采用交互作用。游戏还结合[[角色扮演游戏|角色扮演]]的元素作为升级的设备等。<ref name="ign2015a">{{Citation|last=Silva|first=Marty|title=E3 2015: Abzu's a Stunning Game From the Artist Behind Journey|date=2015-06-22|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2015/06/22/e3-2015-abzus-a-stunning-game-from-the-artist-behind-journey|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate=2016-08-05|archive-date=2016-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160614202456/http://uk.ign.com/articles/2015/06/22/e3-2015-abzus-a-stunning-game-from-the-artist-behind-journey|dead-url=no}}</ref>游戏是以有线性的的进展，而不是开放的世界沙盒，以设计环境並来加以探讨。个别章节的游戏设置在不同的区域海洋，包括洞穴深海洋地区、珊瑚礁和水淹没了一片废墟。<ref>{{Citation|last=Kato|first=Matthew|title=Abzu - Exploring The Mysteries Of The Deep|date=2016-03-05|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/abzu/b/playstation4/archive/2016/03/05/exploring-the-mysteries-of-the-deep.aspx|work=www.gameinformer.com|accessdate=2016-08-05|archive-date=2016-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160803094741/http://www.gameinformer.com/games/abzu/b/playstation4/archive/2016/03/05/exploring-the-mysteries-of-the-deep.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

