rg/web/20171126060212/https://www.polygon.com/2016/12/1/13784410/the-game-awards-winners|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[金摇杆奖|金摇杆奖]]上获得“最佳原创游戏”，“最佳视觉设计”和“年度PlayStation游戏”提名；<ref>{{Cite web|title=Golden Joystick Awards 2016 Winners Announced! – Green Man Gaming Blog|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161128133214/https://www.greenmangaming.com/blog/golden-joystick-awards-2016-winners-announced/|accessdate=2020-03-28|date=2016-11-28|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>在2017年[[BAFTA|BAFTA]]游戏大奖中提名“艺术成就奖”。<ref>{{Citation|title=BAFTA Games Awards 2017 Winners Revealed - IGN|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2017/04/07/bafta-games-awards-2017-winners-revealed|accessdate=2020-03-28|language=en|archive-date=2017-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170420130044/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/04/07/bafta-games-awards-2017-winners-revealed|dead-url=no}}</ref>

